      # What confusion it is causing without the cleaning.

      What confusion it is causing without the cleaning.¶

       
      1.Data cannot be processed and analyzed
      ​
      2.Difficult for non-professionals to understand abbreviations and symbols
      ​
      3.Blanks, redundancy, repetition and incredible answers can affect the results of an analysis

      1.Data cannot be processed and analyzed

      2.Difficult for non-professionals to understand abbreviations and symbols

      3.Blanks, redundancy, repetition and incredible answers can affect the results of an analysis

       
      #   What improvement is it going to have

      What improvement is it going to have¶

       
      1. Eliminate obvious data errors
      ​
      2. Remove symbols
      ​
      3. Unify the unit
      ​
      4. Regrouping data for analysis
      ​
      5. Remove duplicate lines
      ​
      6. Eliminate useless information

      1. Eliminate obvious data errors

      2. Remove symbols

      3. Unify the unit

      4. Regrouping data for analysis

      EVENTS, COMICS, BEAUTY and HOUSE_AND_HOME apps are all free products
